Vehicle Sales in South Africa Rose 12.6% in June From Year Ago, Group Says

-- B y   N a s r e e n   S e r i a
-- 
2011-07-04T09:05:54Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-04/south-african-vehicle-sales-advanced-12-6-last-month-from-previous-year.html
South African vehicle sales rose 12.6
percent in June from a year ago, the National Association of
Automobile Manufacturers of  South Africa  said.  Sales increased to 44,880 last month, the Pretoria-based
association said in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Nasreen Seria at 
 nseria@bloomberg.net  